{"tid":960824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇清一個人之後個心真係好痛","createTime":"2018-12-29T16:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T12:24:47.000Z","uid":228615,"like":9,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96af06f48a92d4f5a9a6e3cfff9d8e6579b3a5d7","tid":960824,"uid":228615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"本身同ex關係好差，一直離離合合都散唔到<br />\n咁岩有次又嘈話分手，個時係真心想分既<br />\n就係呢個時候識左第二個男仔，<br />\n本身淨係諗住同佢做朋友，但佢個時開始追我<br />\n總知好有耐性，日日keep 住穩我同我吹水驚我心情差。<br />\n都暗示過好多次會等我之類，<br />\n但我個時真係對愛情冇信心，都無辦法一分手就同第二個一齊，咁keep 住傾左個半個月啦，我都覺得可以比個機會大家既，點知佢話要溫書大家收左嗲<br />\n直到最近發現佢同人一齊左。。。。。。<br />\n點解明明當時講到實牙實齒咁，你等唔到你講啊麻扮咩等到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而嘉更加覺得唔再信愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89eb667d1ed2b892393259afe4b074c52852ee04","tid":960824,"uid":228266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"騎牛溫馬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2825749bd18b4b0ab52395d64465ce12d8384ed2","tid":960824,"uid":228266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"搵"},{"pid":"d8b9f1620da0e451380e4bc4e6a1c3bc55ba2fd8","tid":960824,"uid":228615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89eb667d1ed2b892393259afe4b074c52852ee04","tid":960824,"uid":228266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"騎牛溫馬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"做唔到，之前同ex一齊想諗過咁做但過唔到自己"},{"pid":"cb4f28dc1941bbcaaacc924deea9fd60090238e1","tid":960824,"uid":217774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"屌，你有冇叫人俾啲時間你"},{"pid":"aa4cb07d96ae31d7f95a792157be60fcdede9a1b","tid":960824,"uid":228606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，追唔到你咪搵第二個